pnpm-lock.yaml
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
# Exception: packages/sdk/package-lock.json is the SOURCE OF TRUTH for
# the Greenfield JS bridge versions used by both local dev AND the
# Docker image's `npm ci`. Without it committed, the Dockerfile build
# fails with "package-lock.json missing", and worse — version drift
# between Mac and Linux silently re-introduces the kind of "v1 vs v2
# of @bnb-chain/greenfield-js-sdk" bug that broke production once.
!packages/sdk/package-lock.json

